data.description: Be impressed the moment you arrive at this beautiful brick 3 bedroom, 2 bath raised ranch with side driveway leading to the 2-car garage and large back yard that's perfect for entertaining. Enter inside to the spacious living room with ultra-modern tray ceiling. Bedrooms have gleaming hardwood floors, and the bright eat-in kitchen boast granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and tons of cabinets. Did I mention entertainment? Welcome downstairs to a full finished basement with a bar and decorative fireplace. The huge laundry room comes complete with a washer, dryer and compact freezer. This is a rare gem with new water heater, furnace and AC condenser! Near to expressway, public transportation, school, park and civic center. Believe me this home won't last long. See today!
